  "body": "<h1 style=\"font-weight: 900; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.3em;\">Monkee</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  Reimagine villagers and iron golems as playful monkeys, bringing a fun and lively twist to your Minecraft world.\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 800; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">🛠️ Features</h2>\n<ul style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto; padding-left: 1.2em; list-style-type: disc;\">\n  <li>Villagers transformed to HalloJost skin</li>\n  <li>Textures: Villagers</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">🎨 Style</h2>\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  A rework of Minecraft villagers in the style of <strong>HalloJost skin</strong>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto; font-style: italic; text-align: center;\">\n  Reimagine villagers and iron golems as playful <strong>Monkee</strong>, bringing a fun and lively twist to your Minecraft world.\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">📝 Versions</h2>\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  <strong>Version:</strong> <code>1.0</code> <em>(beta)</em>\n</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 3em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; text-align: center; font-weight: 900;\">➕ Other Projects</h2>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;\">\n  <tr>\n\t<td style=\"padding: 1em; width: 140px; height: 160px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><strong>Essentials Style</div>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/essentials-style\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/8zAhdB4V/f73795cb02b0e975192d6a2492717ea70c99459d.png\" alt=\"Essentials Style\" width=\"96\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n      </a>\n    </td>\n  